latestIgtvVideos.title: Relishing Haleem at Paradise 😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Season of Haleem is back !!! 😍 Missed Having haleem due to pandemic the entire last year and realised Paradise started serving Haleem at various stores and decided to order it through their own online delivery app which is available on both playstore & iOS. 👈 The app is totally user friendly and easy to use and has some great offers. 
First things first, the packaging is absolutely friendly and tamper proof. Very easy to carry & easy to eat directly from it. 
Being a renowned brand, Paradise is synonymous with TRUST and they emphasise on Stringent cleanliness, hygiene & safety at all stages of Operation. 
The Taste of Haleem has not changed since years. Made of Finest Ingredients, this is pure #ParadiseWaliFeeling. 

Here’s an interesting contest for all you folks. Click a picture of Paradise Haleem and post it and tag me & @paradisefoodcourt with the hashtags #ParadiseWaliFeeling #ParadiseHaleem #ParadiseHyderabad. 3 of the lucky winners will win free haleem at the end of the contest !
